vote.title: A resolution authorizing an increase in the joint election agreement and election services contract between the City of Dallas, Dallas County, and various other jurisdictions within Dallas County, for the conduct of a runoff election to be held Saturday, June 5, 2021 - Not to exceed $1,475,551.53, from $1,650,190.14 to $3,125,741.67 - Financing: General Fund (see Fiscal Information)
